@node ce Copyrights

 @{b}Move2.1@{ub} is Freeware. That allows you to spread it wherever you want for
 free, when the following things are unchanged included:

  @{b}Move2.1@{ub} (the directory with Icon)
  @{b}Move2.1@{ub} (the command, of course!)
