 You are not allowed to change any contents of one of the included files.
@endnode
@node he History

 - V2.1 Moves files und their icons. Moves now also whole directories and
        their icons. Knows, if the target already exists, if the target
        is the same as the source, if the arguments are missing and no
        target is set.
        Helpfuntion and delete-only-funtion included. Better design and new
        bilingual manual.
        [ by Zito/Zetec ]

 - V2.0 Moves files and their icons and deletes the sources. (Also only
        single ones. It`s so a second beta, but optimized and with new
        design!) With manual!
        [ by Zito/Zetec ]

 - V1.4 Moves now really files and their icons und deletes the source, but
        only single files yet.
        [ by CDP ]

 - V1.0 Only a beta, which doesn`t operate right, wether back nor front.
        [ by CDP ]
@endnode
